text: antima ghaligeya kuritada jnanavu avana (allahana) vasadalle ide. Avanige arivillade yava hannu tanna goneyinda hora hom'malaradu, yava hennu garbha dharisalaralu mattu prasavisalaralu. ‘‘Elliddare nanna paludararu?’’ Endu a dina avanu avarodane kugi keluvanu. Avaru heluvaru; ‘‘navu ninage tilisiruvevu, nam'mallobbaru adara samarthakaralla’’
